properties.Name: StoreDisplaySection
properties.Description: A grocery store/department aisle is divided into Rows.

Columns.Name: StoreId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Store.

Columns.Name: SectionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Row.

Columns.Name: AisleId
Columns.Description:
The unique identifier of an Aisle.

An Aisle is the space between storage devices that is used by material handlers for access.

Columns.Name: LocationAddress
Columns.Description: A unique address within a Warehouse that may identify a Building, Storeroom, Area, Aisle, Shelf, Tier, Bin etc.

Columns.Name: FloorLocationXCoordinate
Columns.Description: The floor location x-coordinate of the Row.

Columns.Name: FloorLocationYCoordinate
Columns.Description: The floor location y-coordinate of the Row.

Columns.Name: SectionLength
Columns.Description: The length of the section measured in the unit of measure specified by the Unit of Measure ID.

Columns.Name: SectionHeight
Columns.Description: The height of the section measured in the unit of measure specified by the Unit of Measure ID.
